| Cascade Type          | What it Does                                       |
| --------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| `CascadeType.PERSIST` | Saves child automatically when parent is saved     |
| `CascadeType.MERGE`   | Updates child automatically when parent is updated |
| `CascadeType.REMOVE`  | Deletes child automatically when parent is deleted |
| `CascadeType.REFRESH` | Refreshes child when parent refreshed              |
| `CascadeType.DETACH`  | Detaches child when parent detached                |
| `CascadeType.ALL`     | Applies all above (save, update, delete, etc.)     |
